# =============================================================================
# TRINITY HIVE SWARM — Cookie Pool Configuration
# =============================================================================
# Extract cookies from your browser: DevTools > Application > Cookies > gemini.google.com
# Each slot represents one Google account from your Family Sharing plan.
#
# Slot 1 = LEADER (used for MoE synthesis / judging)
# Slots 2-6 = WORKERS (used for parallel generation)
# =============================================================================

